com.facebook.buck.core.graph.transformation.executor

Interface DepsAwareExecutor<ResultType,TaskType extends DepsAwareTask<ResultType,TaskType>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultDepsAwareExecutor

    public interface DepsAwareExecutor<ResultType,TaskType extends DepsAwareTask<ResultType,TaskType>>
    A specialized Executor that executes DepsAwareTask. This executor will attempt to maintain maximum concurrency, while completing dependencies of each supplied work first.

    It is guaranteed that the dependencies from DepsAwareTask.getDepsSupplier() will be completed before the work itself is executed.

    In terms of thread safety, it is guaranteed that for the same DepsAwareTask, its deps supplier from DepsAwareTask.getDepsSupplier() will be executed before its callable from DepsAwareTask.getCallable() is executed. That is, the supplier execution "happens before" the callable execution, but potentially in different threads, where "happens before" is the standard event ordering a -> b. There is an at least once guarantee on the number of invocations of the deps supplier, and an exactly once guarantee on the callable. There is no guarantee of synchronization between different instances of DepsAwareTask other than that its dependencies will be completed before the callable is evaluated.
